          </p>
          
          <p class="text-body-lg text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
            Professional fire damage restoration is essential—not just to rebuild, but to ensure your property is safe and free from hidden hazards. Soot is acidic and corrosive, continuing to cause damage long after the flames are out. Smoke particles penetrate deep into materials, releasing toxins and odors for months if not properly addressed.
          </p>
        </div>
        
