            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Fire Damage</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-brand-gray">Charring, melting, and structural damage from direct flame contact. Requires careful assessment and reconstruction.</p>
