              6
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-display-sm text-brand-black mb-2">Reconstruction & Restoration</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mb-4">
                The final phase involves rebuilding damaged structures and restoring your property to its pre-fire condition—or better. From drywall to flooring to complete room rebuilds.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
                  <Icon name="check-circle" size="sm" class="text-brand-orange flex-shrink-0" />
                  Structural repairs
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-body-sm text-brand-gray">
