  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-display-lg text-brand-black mb-6">
            Content Cleaning & Restoration
          </h2>
          
          <p class="text-body-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
            Fire doesn't just damage your building—it affects everything inside. Many items that appear ruined can actually be professionally cleaned and restored. We handle your belongings with care, saving what we can and documenting what we can't for your insurance claim.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-brand-cream-200 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-orange text-white flex items-center justify-center">
